text: Petropavlovo () is a rural locality (a selo) in Starokamyshlinsky Selsoviet, Kushnarenkovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 43 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 42 km from Kushnarenkovo, 13 km from Starye Kamyshly. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kushnarenkovsky District
title: Petropavlovo
